#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ksudoku; is a logic-based symbol placement puzzle."
msgstr "&ksudoku; je logična uganka o postavljanju simbolov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The player has to fill a grid with symbols so that each column, row and "
"block on the game board contains only one instance of each symbol. In "
"&ksudoku; the symbols are usually the numbers 1 to 9, but may be the letters "
"A to P or A to Y in larger puzzles. Puzzles start with the board partially "
"filled and it is your job to fill in the rest. Some types of puzzle have "
"less than nine symbols."
msgstr ""
"Igralec mora zapolniti mrežo s simboli, tako da vsak stolpec, vrstica in "
"blok na igralni plošči vsebuje samo en primerek vsakega simbola. V &ksudoku; "
"so simboli običajno številke od 1 do 9, lahko pa so črke od A do P ali A do "
"Y v večjih ugankah. Uganke se začnejo z delno zapolnjeno tablo, vaša naloga "
"pa je, da izpolnite preostanek. Nekatere vrste sestavljank imajo manj kot "
"devet simbolov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start a game, you can choose from several Sudoku types and sizes. "
"You can then have &ksudoku; generate a puzzle for you to solve or you can "
"start with an empty board and enter in a puzzle from another source, such as "
"a newspaper, then get &ksudoku; to check it and maybe solve it."
msgstr ""
"Ko začnete igro, lahko izbirate med več vrstami in velikostmi Sudokuja. Nato "
"imate lahko &ksudoku; ustvarite uganko, ki jo boste rešili, lahko pa začnete "
"s prazno tablo in vnesete uganko iz drugega vira, kot je časopis, nato pa "
"dobite &ksudoku; za preveriti in morda rešiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are many variations of Sudoku in existence and &ksudoku; provides a "
"good selection of them. The most common type, Standard Sudoku, has a 9x9 "
"square grid and uses Arabic numerals 1 to 9 as symbols. The grid has 9 rows "
"and 9 columns and is divided into 9 blocks of 3x3 squares. The problem is – "
"each symbol can only be used once per row, column or block."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja veliko različic Sudokuja in &ksudoku; ponuja dober izbor le-teh. "
"Najpogostejši tip, standardni sudoku, ima kvadratno mrežo 9x9 in uporablja "
"arabske številke od 1 do 9 kot simbole. Mreža ima 9 vrstic in 9 stolpcev ter "
"je razdeljena na 9 blokov kvadratov 3x3. Težava je v tem, da je vsak simbol "
"mogoče uporabiti samo enkrat na vrstico, stolpec ali blok."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It takes time and concentration to complete a game. However, solving Sudoku "
"puzzles helps to increase overall brain activity and therefore is highly "
"recommended."
msgstr ""
"Za dokončanje igre sta potrebna čas in koncentracija. Vendar pa reševanje "
"sudokujev pomaga povečati celotno možgansko aktivnost in je zato zelo "
"priporočljivo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fill the grid so that each column, row and block contains only one instance "
"of each symbol."
msgstr ""
"Izpolnite mrežo tako, da vsak stolpec, vrstica in blok vsebuje samo en "
"primerek posameznega simbola."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the game starts you are prompted to choose which game type and board "
"size you are interested in. You can enter in a puzzle from another source or "
"have &ksudoku; generate a puzzle. The generator has several difficulty "
"settings and some symmetry settings, which affect the pattern in which the "
"puzzle is generated. Your game experience will depend on which of all these "
"options you choose."
msgstr ""
"Ko se igra začne, boste pozvani, da izberete, katera vrsta igre in velikost "
"plošče vas zanimata. Lahko vstopite v sestavljanko iz drugega vira ali imate "
"&ksudoku; ustvari sestavljanko. Generator ima več težavnostnih nastavitev in "
"nekaj nastavitev simetrije, ki vplivajo na vzorec, v katerem je uganka "
"ustvarjena. Vaša igralna izkušnja bo odvisna od tega, katero od vseh teh "
"možnosti izberete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the puzzle board appears, take a look at the left hand side. There is a "
"selection list which contains all the symbols available in the current game. "
"The set of symbols depends on the size of game you choose. Games may have 4, "
"9, 16 or 25 symbols. The first two sets use the numbers 1 to 4 or 1 to 9: "
"the others use the letters A to P or A to Y."
msgstr ""
"Ko se prikaže tabla z ugankami, poglejte na levo stran. Obstaja izbirni "
"seznam, ki vsebuje vse simbole, ki so na voljo v trenutni igri. Nabor "
"simbolov je odvisen od velikosti igre, ki jo izberete. Igre imajo lahko 4, "
"9, 16 ali 25 simbolov. Prva dva sklopa uporabljata številke od 1 do 4 ali od "
"1 do 9: drugi uporabljajo črke od A do P ali od A do Y."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, note the boundaries in the game board. The thick lines outline the "
"blocks. Each of these blocks has to be completed using the symbols available "
"and each symbol must be used once and only once within the block. The same "
"is true of the rows and columns in the board."
msgstr ""
"Najprej si zapomnite meje na igralni plošči. Debele črte označujejo bloke. "
"Vsak od teh blokov je treba izpolniti z razpoložljivimi simboli in vsak "
"simbol je treba uporabiti enkrat in samo enkrat v bloku. Enako velja za "
"vrstice in stolpce na tabli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now you can start entering symbols into the vacant squares on the board. To "
"do that, select the symbol you wish to enter from the selection list on the "
"left, then use the mouse to click on a vacant square in the board. "
"Alternatively, you can hover with the mouse over a vacant square or use the "
"cursor keys to move around, then use the keyboard to enter a symbol."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj lahko začnete vnašati simbole v prazna polja na tabli. To storite tako, "
"da iz izbirnega seznama na levi izberete simbol, ki ga želite vnesti, nato "
"pa z miško kliknete na prazno polje na plošči. Druga možnost je, da se z "
"miško pomaknete nad prazen kvadrat ali uporabite smerne tipke za premikanje, "
"nato pa uporabite tipkovnico za vnos simbola."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In Roxdoku (three-dimensional) puzzles, always use the mouse to set a small "
"cube to a value and use a <emphasis>double</emphasis> click. When you rotate "
"the large cube, by clicking and dragging with the mouse, it is easier to see "
"what values are on the small cubes in the background if you click "
"<emphasis>between</emphasis> the small cubes, not on them."
msgstr ""
"V Roxdoku (tridimenzionalnih) ugankah vedno uporabite miško, da nastavite "
"majhno kocko na vrednost in uporabite <emphasis>dvojni</emphasis> klik. Ko "
"vrtite veliko kocko s klikanjem in vlečenjem z miško, je lažje videti, "
"katere vrednosti so na majhnih kockah v ozadju, če kliknete <emphasis>med</"
"emphasis> malimi kockami, ne nanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is useful sometimes to enter markers or notes, which are tiny symbols "
"within a square. These have no influence on the solution, but they can help "
"you keep track of ideas you have had, especially when there is a choice "
"between two alternatives and you do not yet have enough information to "
"decide between them. To enter a marker or note, click with the &RMB; or hold "
"down the &Shift; key when using the keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Včasih je koristno vnesti oznake ali opombe, ki so drobni simboli v "
"kvadratu. Ti nimajo vpliva na rešitev, lahko pa vam pomagajo slediti idejam, "
"ki ste jih imeli, še posebej, ko obstaja izbira med dvema alternativama in "
"še nimate dovolj informacij, da bi se odločili med njima. Če želite vnesti "
"oznako ali opombo, kliknite z &RMB; ali držite &Shift; tipko pri uporabi "
"tipkovnice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To clear symbols from a square, hover over the square with the mouse and hit "
"&Del; or &Backspace; on the keyboard or click with the &RMB; on the square."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrisati simbole iz kvadrata, se z miško pomaknite nad kvadrat in "
"pritisnite &Del; ali &Backspace; na tipkovnici ali kliknite z &RMB; na trgu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Notice that the squares change color while you hover the mouse over them. "
"This is to help you keep up with the rules of &ksudoku;. Use the vertical "
"and horizontal lines to check if the symbol you are about to enter into a "
"vacant spot is already in use anywhere in the vertical or horizontal line "
"that square is a part of. The coloring also highlights the block which, if "
"you remember, must also contain only one instance of each symbol. If you do "
"not need the highlighting, you can use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &ksudoku;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item to turn it off."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da kvadratki spreminjajo barvo, medtem ko miško premikate nad "
"njimi. To vam bo pomagalo slediti pravilom &ksudoku;. Z navpičnimi in "
"vodoravnimi črtami preverite, ali je simbol, ki ga boste vnesli na prazno "
"mesto, že v uporabi kjer koli v navpični ali vodoravni črti, katere del je "
"ta kvadrat. Barvanje poudarja tudi blok, ki mora, če se spomnite, prav tako "
"vsebovati samo en primerek posameznega simbola. Če označevanja ne "
"potrebujete, lahko uporabite menijski element "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &ksudoku;"
"…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da ga izklopite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep entering symbols in accordance with the rules until the whole game "
"field is filled up. At this point &ksudoku; will check if all the entries "
"are valid and will either correct you or accept your solution."
msgstr ""
"Vnašajte simbole v skladu s pravili, dokler ni zapolnjeno celotno igralno "
"polje. Na tej točki &ksudoku; preveri, ali so vsi vnosi veljavni, in vas "
"popravi ali sprejme vašo rešitev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Game Rules"
msgstr "Splošna pravila igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "The rules of &ksudoku; are quite simple."
msgstr "Pravila &ksudoku; so precej preprosta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Depending on the size of the game board, the type of puzzle and the "
"difficulty level chosen an individual &ksudoku; puzzle may take from a few "
"minutes to a few hours to solve."
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od velikosti igralne plošče, vrste uganke in težavnostne stopnje, "
"izbrani posamezni &ksudoku; rešitev uganke lahko traja od nekaj minut do "
"nekaj ur."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each square may hold one and only one symbol."
msgstr "Vsak kvadrat lahko vsebuje en in samo en simbol."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each horizontal row (as defined by the game board) can contain each symbol "
"exactly once."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka vodoravna vrstica (kot je določena z igralno ploščo) lahko vsebuje "
"vsak simbol natanko enkrat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each vertical column (as defined by the game board) can contain each symbol "
"exactly once."
msgstr ""
"Vsak navpični stolpec (kot ga določa igralna plošča) lahko vsebuje vsak "
"simbol natanko enkrat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each block (as defined by the game board) can contain each symbol exactly "
"once"
msgstr ""
"Vsak blok (kot ga določa igralna plošča) lahko vsebuje vsak simbol natanko "
"enkrat"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:193 index.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "Opomba:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "The set of symbols depends on the size of game you choose."
msgstr "Nabor simbolov je odvisen od velikosti igre, ki jo izberete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Knowledge of mathematics or language is not required to solve &ksudoku; "
"puzzles, but a little ability with arithmetic is needed in Killer Sudoku and "
"Mathdoku puzzles."
msgstr ""
"Za reševanje &ksudoku; ni potrebno znanje matematike ali jezika. uganke, "
"vendar je pri ugankah Killer Sudoku in Mathdoku potrebno malo spretnosti z "
"aritmetiko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The symbols already on the game board when the puzzle starts cannot be "
"changed."
msgstr ""
"Simbolov, ki so že na igralni plošči, ko se uganka začne, ni mogoče "
"spremeniti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can only modify the symbols you have previously entered."
msgstr "Spremenite lahko samo simbole, ki ste jih predhodno vnesli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Puzzles generated by &ksudoku; have one solution only."
msgstr "Uganke, ki jih ustvari &ksudoku; imajo samo eno rešitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Puzzles you enter in might have no solution or more than one solution, but "
"if they are from a published source this probably means you have made a data-"
"entry error."
msgstr ""
"Uganke, ki jih vnesete, morda nimajo rešitve ali pa imajo več kot eno "
"rešitev, vendar če so iz objavljenega vira, to verjetno pomeni, da ste "
"naredili napako pri vnosu podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ksudoku; Variations"
msgstr "&ksudoku; Različice"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sudoku Puzzles"
msgstr "Sudoku uganke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Standard 9x9 Sudoku puzzle has 9 rows, 9 columns and 9 square blocks of "
"size 3x3."
msgstr ""
"Standardna uganka Sudoku 9x9 ima 9 vrstic, 9 stolpcev in 9 kvadratnih blokov "
"velikosti 3x3."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Other sizes of Standard Sudoku are 4x4 (very easy), 16x16 and 25x25 (not so "
"easy)."
msgstr ""
"Druge velikosti standardnega sudokuja so 4x4 (zelo enostavno), 16x16 in "
"25x25 (ne tako enostavno)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Jigsaw and Aztec variations are the same as Standard 9x9 Sudoku except "
"that some blocks are not square."
msgstr ""
"Različici Jigsaw in Aztec sta enaki kot standardni sudoku 9x9, le da "
"nekateri bloki niso kvadratni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The XSudoku variation is exactly the same as Standard Sudoku with an "
"additional requirement: the two main diagonals must also each contain the "
"symbols 1 to 9 once and once only. &ksudoku; highlights the diagonals to "
"make this easier to see."
msgstr ""
"Različica XSudoku je popolnoma enaka standardnemu sudokuju z dodatno "
"zahtevo: obe glavni diagonali morata prav tako vsebovati simbole od 1 do 9 "
"enkrat in samo enkrat. &ksudoku; poudari diagonale, da je to lažje videti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Nonomino 9x9, Pentomino 5x5 and Tetromino 4x4 variations are the same as "
"a Standard Sudoku except that some blocks are not square."
msgstr ""
"Različice Nonomino 9x9, Pentomino 5x5 in Tetromino 4x4 so enake kot "
"standardni sudoku, le da nekateri bloki niso kvadratni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The 6x6 variation is the same as a Standard Sudoku except that the blocks "
"are six 3x2 rectangles."
msgstr ""
"Različica 6x6 je enaka standardnemu sudokuju, le da so bloki šest "
"pravokotnikov 3x2."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Samurai Puzzles"
msgstr "Samurajske uganke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Samurai Sudoku consists of five Standard Sudoku puzzles of 9x9 squares "
"each, overlapping at the corners by four 3x3 blocks. Each of the five "
"puzzles has 9 rows, 9 columns and 9 blocks to solve and the symbols in the "
"overlapping squares must fit into the solutions of two Standard 9x9 Sudokus."
msgstr ""
"Samuraiski Sudoku je sestavljen iz petih standardnih ugank Sudoku, vsaka po "
"9x9 kvadratov, ki se na vogalih prekrivajo s štirimi bloki 3x3. Vsaka od "
"petih ugank ima 9 vrstic, 9 stolpcev in 9 blokov, ki jih je treba rešiti, "
"simboli v prekrivajočih se kvadratih pa se morajo ujemati z rešitvami dveh "
"standardnih sudokujev 9x9."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Tiny Samurai Sudoku contains five 4x4 Sudoku puzzles, overlapping at the "
"corners by four squares. Each of the five puzzles has 4 rows, 4 columns and "
"4 blocks to solve."
msgstr ""
"Mali Samuraijski Sudoku vsebuje pet ugank 4x4 Sudoku, ki se na vogalih "
"prekrivajo s štirimi kvadratki. Vsaka od petih ugank ima 4 vrstice, 4 "
"stolpce in 4 bloke, ki jih je treba rešiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Windmill variation consists of five Standard 9x9 Sudoku puzzles, "
"overlapping at the corners by two 3x3 blocks. It is like a Samurai Sudoku, "
"but the central 9x9 Sudoku is harder to see. Eight of its 3x3 blocks are "
"shared with the sails of the windmill and only the central 3x3 block is not."
msgstr ""
"Različica Mlin na veter je sestavljena iz petih standardnih sudokujev 9x9, "
"ki se na vogalih prekrivajo z dvema blokoma 3x3. Je kot samurajski sudoku, "
"vendar je osrednji sudoku 9x9 težje videti. Osem njenih blokov 3x3 si deli z "
"jadri mlina na veter in samo osrednji blok 3x3 ne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Sohei variation is another Samurai type and has four 9x9 Sudoku puzzles, "
"overlapping at two corners by a 3x3 block. The central 3x3 block of the "
"puzzle is empty."
msgstr ""
"Različica Sohei je še en samurajski tip in ima štiri uganke Sudoku 9x9, ki "
"se na dveh vogalih prekrivajo z blokom 3x3. Osrednji blok 3x3 sestavljanke "
"je prazen."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid "Roxdoku 3D Puzzles"
msgstr "Roxdoku 3D uganke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Roxdoku variants are based on cubes in three dimensions, but are easier "
"than they sound. There are no rows or columns. A 3x3x3 Roxdoku puzzle has 27 "
"small cubes arranged into a larger 3x3x3 cube. This contains nine slices, "
"each containing 3x3 small cubes, and these are the square blocks that must "
"be filled with the numbers 1 to 9. A 4x4x4 Roxdoku has twelve 4x4 slices and "
"a 5x5x5 Roxdoku has fifteen 5x5 slices."
msgstr ""
"Različice Roxdoku temeljijo na kockah v treh dimenzijah, vendar so lažje, "
"kot se sliši. Ni vrstic ali stolpcev. Sestavljanka Roxdoku 3x3x3 ima 27 "
"majhnih kock, razporejenih v večjo kocko 3x3x3. Ta vsebuje devet rezin, od "
"katerih vsaka vsebuje 3x3 majhne kocke, in to so kvadratni bloki, ki morajo "
"biti izpolnjeni s številkami od 1 do 9. Roxdoku 4x4x4 ima dvanajst rezin "
"4x4, Roxdoku 5x5x5 pa petnajst rezin 5x5."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Roxdoku Twin variant has two 3x3x3 Roxdoku puzzles sharing a corner. The "
"corner piece must be part of the solution of both 3x3x3 cubes."
msgstr ""
"Različica Roxdoku Twin ima dve uganki Roxdoku velikosti 3x3x3, ki si delita "
"vogal. Kotni del mora biti del rešitve obeh kock 3x3x3."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Double Roxdoku variant contains two 3x3x3 Roxdoku puzzles sharing three "
"pieces along an edge. The edge pieces must be part of the solution of both "
"3x3x3 cubes."
msgstr ""
"Različica Double Roxdoku vsebuje dve uganki Roxdoku velikosti 3x3x3, ki si "
"delita tri dele vzdolž roba. Robovi morajo biti del rešitve obeh kock 3x3x3."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Samurai Roxdoku variant has nine 3x3x3 Roxdoku puzzles. One is at the "
"center and the other eight 3x3x3 cubes overlap it, one at each of the "
"central cube's corners. Those corner pieces must each be part of the "
"solution of two 3x3x3 cubes."
msgstr ""
"Različica Samurai Roxdoku ima devet ugank 3x3x3 Roxdoku. Ena je v središču, "
"ostalih osem kock 3x3x3 pa se prekriva z njo, po ena na vsakem vogalu "
"osrednje kocke. Vsak od teh vogalnih kosov mora biti del rešitve dveh kock "
"3x3x3."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Killer and Mathdoku Variations"
msgstr "Variacije Killer in Mathdoku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Killer puzzles have two variants: Tiny Killer (4x4) and Killer Sudoku (9x9). "
"They both have rows, columns and square blocks, exactly as in Standard "
"Sudoku puzzles and following exactly the same rules. They also have "
"irregularly shaped areas called cages, where each cage's digits must add up "
"to the number in small type in the corner of the cage and no digit can be "
"repeated within the cage. Typically the puzzle starts with only a few "
"squares containing symbols. You need to use arithmetic and the usual Sudoku "
"rules together to work out the solution. The screen graphics make it "
"difficult to visualize the square blocks that are present, but they are "
"easier to see if you print the puzzle, using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Ubijalske uganke imajo dve različici: Tiny Killer (4x4) in Killer Sudoku "
"(9x9). Oba imata vrstice, stolpce in kvadratne bloke, natanko tako kot v "
"standardnih sudoku ugankah in po popolnoma enakih pravilih. Imajo tudi "
"področja nepravilne oblike, imenovane kletke, kjer se morajo števke vsake "
"kletke sešteti z majhnim številom v kotu kletke in nobena števka se ne sme "
"ponoviti v kletki. Običajno se sestavljanka začne z le nekaj kvadratki, ki "
"vsebujejo simbole. Za rešitev morate uporabiti aritmetiko in običajna "
"pravila Sudokuja. Zaslonska grafika otežuje vizualizacijo prisotnih "
"kvadratnih blokov, vendar jih je lažje videti, če natisnete sestavljanko z "
"uporabo elementa menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Igre</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Natisni…</guimenuitem ></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mathdoku variants, also known as <trademark>Kenken</trademark>, have no "
"blocks, only row and column restrictions, and have cages where the digits "
"must add, subtract, divide or multiply according to the values and "
"arithmetical symbols in small type in their corners. A digit in a Mathdoku "
"cage can be repeated, but not in the same column or row. For example, an L-"
"shape of three squares with a requirement 5+ can have solutions 1 3 1 or 2 1 "
"2, provided the ones or twos are not in the same row or column as each "
"other. Note that subtraction and division cages always have two squares and "
"the two digits of the solution can appear in either order. For example, a 2-"
"cage could have solutions 1 3 or 3 1 or 2 4 or 4 2, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Različice Mathdokuja, znane tudi kot <trademark>Kenken</trademark>, nimajo "
"blokov, ampak le omejitve vrstic in stolpcev, in imajo kletke, kjer morajo "
"števke seštevati, odštevati, deliti ali množiti glede na vrednosti in "
"aritmetične simbole v majhni pisavi njihovih kotičkih. Števka v kletki "
"Mathdoku se lahko ponovi, vendar ne v istem stolpcu ali vrstici. Na primer, "
"oblika L treh kvadratov z zahtevo 5+ ima lahko rešitve 1 3 1 ali 2 1 2, pod "
"pogojem, da enice ali dve niso v isti vrstici ali stolpcu. Upoštevajte, da "
"imajo kletke za odštevanje in deljenje vedno dva kvadrata in dve števki "
"rešitve sta lahko prikazani v katerem koli vrstnem redu. Na primer, 2-kletka "
"bi lahko imela rešitve 1 3 ali 3 1 ali 2 4 ali 4 2, itd."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Because there are no blocks in a Mathdoku puzzle, it can have any size from "
"3x3 up to 9x9, with the default being 6x6. See the <link linkend="
"\"configuration\">Game Configuration</link> section for details. To get you "
"started, there is a variant called Mathdoku 101 of size 4x4."
msgstr ""
"Ker v uganki Mathdoku ni blokov, je lahko poljubne velikosti od 3x3 do 9x9, "
"privzeto pa je 6x6. Za podrobnosti glejte razdelek <link linkend="
"\"configuration\">Konfiguracija igre</link>. Za lažji začetek je na voljo "
"različica Mathdoku 101 velikosti 4x4."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "Take your time and do not rush. &ksudoku; is not a quick game."
msgstr "Vzemite si čas in ne hitite. &ksudoku; ni hitra igra."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pay attention to the row, column, and block colorings. They are there to "
"help you."
msgstr ""
"Bodite pozorni na barve vrstic, stolpcev in blokov. Tam so, da vam pomagajo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure that no duplicate symbol exists already in the row, column or "
"block where you are entering a symbol."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da v vrstici, stolpcu ali bloku, kamor vnašate simbol, že ni "
"podvojenega simbola."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If in doubt, try to foresee if a square you are entering a symbol into may "
"be needed by some other symbol, which otherwise cannot go anywhere else due "
"to the row, column and block rules."
msgstr ""
"Če ste v dvomih, poskusite predvideti, ali kvadratek, v katerega vnašate "
"simbol, morda potrebuje kakšen drug simbol, ki sicer ne more iti nikamor "
"drugam zaradi pravil vrstic, stolpcev in blokov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the Internet to search for general hints and strategies for solving "
"Sudoku puzzles."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite internet za iskanje splošnih namigov in strategij za reševanje "
"sudokujev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use marker moves when you spot a square or squares that have just a few "
"alternatives but you cannot decide between them immediately. Markers will "
"save you time and memory effort later, when more squares have been filled "
"in. See <link linkend=\"howto\"> How to Play</link> for details of how to "
"use markers."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite poteze označevalcev, ko opazite polje ali polja, ki imajo le nekaj "
"možnosti, vendar se ne morete takoj odločiti med njimi. Označevalci vam bodo "
"pozneje, ko bo izpolnjenih več kvadratkov, prihranili čas in spomin. Glejte "
"<link linkend=\"howto\">Kako igrati</link> za podrobnosti o uporabi "
"označevalcev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are having trouble, try to retrace your steps and see exactly where "
"you have made an error. You can use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Move</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and <menuchoice><guimenu>Move</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu items, repeatedly "
"if necessary, and there is a setting in <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &ksudoku;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> that "
"highlights errors."
msgstr ""
"Če imate težave, poskusite slediti svojim korakom in natančno ugotovite, kje "
"ste naredili napako. Uporabite lahko <menuchoice><guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uveljavi</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice > elementi menija, večkrat, če je potrebno, in obstaja nastavitev "
"v <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&ksudoku;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, ki osvetli napake."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Even though &ksudoku; provides a 'Hint' option for you, try not to use it "
"often. Remember, solving the puzzle all by yourself enhances your brain "
"activity, while using the 'Hint' feature too often is cheating."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav &ksudoku; ponuja možnost 'Namig', je poskusite ne uporabljati "
"pogosto. Ne pozabite, da samostojno reševanje uganke izboljša vašo možgansko "
"aktivnost, medtem ko je prepogosta uporaba funkcije »Namig« goljufanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have too much trouble solving a certain puzzle and simply must use "
"the 'Hint' feature, then maybe you should try decreasing the difficulty "
"level, or try a simpler, more basic puzzle."
msgstr ""
"Če imate preveč težav z reševanjem določene uganke in preprosto morate "
"uporabiti funkcijo 'Namig', potem bi morda morali poskusiti znižati "
"težavnostno stopnjo ali poskusiti s preprostejšo, bolj osnovno uganko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some puzzle layouts feature very specific game board shapes. It is a good "
"idea to have the highlighting option enabled even if you consider yourself "
"an experienced player."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere postavitve ugank imajo zelo specifične oblike igralnih plošč. Dobro "
"je imeti možnost označevanja omogočeno, tudi če se imate za izkušenega "
"igralca."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "Pregled vmesnika"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Welcome Screen"
msgstr "Pozdravni zaslon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Welcome Screen is the first thing you see when you start &ksudoku; or "
"use the toolbar or menu to request a new game. It has a list of all the "
"puzzle types and sizes and you can click on one of them to make a selection."
msgstr ""
"Pozdravni zaslon je prva stvar, ki jo vidite, ko zaženete &ksudoku; ali "
"uporabite orodno vrstico ali meni, da zahtevate novo igro. Ima seznam vseh "
"vrst in velikosti uganke in lahko kliknete eno od njih, da izberete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click the button marked <guibutton>Enter In A Puzzle</guibutton>, an "
"empty board of the selected type and size appears. Here you can use the "
"mouse or keyboard to enter in a puzzle from another source, such as a "
"newspaper. When you have finished, use the <guilabel>Check</guilabel> "
"action, on toolbar or menu, to check the puzzle. It should have just one "
"solution. If so, you can start solving the puzzle or perhaps get &ksudoku; "
"to solve it. If there is no solution or more than one solution, it probably "
"means you have made a data-entry error somewhere."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete gumb z oznako <guibutton>Vstopi v uganko</guibutton>, se prikaže "
"prazna tabla izbrane vrste in velikosti. Tukaj lahko z miško ali tipkovnico "
"vstopite v uganko iz drugega vira, kot je časopis. Ko končate, uporabite "
"dejanje <guilabel>Preveri</guilabel> v orodni vrstici ali meniju, da "
"preverite uganko. Imeti mora samo eno rešitev. Če je tako, lahko začnete "
"reševati uganko ali morda uspete &ksudoku; rešiti. Če rešitve ni ali jih je "
"več kot ena, verjetno pomeni, da ste nekje naredili napako pri vnosu "
"podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click the button marked <guibutton>Generate A Puzzle</guibutton>, "
"&ksudoku; will display a board with some squares already filled in. It is up "
"to you to fill in the rest."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete gumb <guibutton>Ustvari uganko</guibutton>, &ksudoku; bo "
"prikazala tablo z nekaterimi kvadratki, ki so že izpolnjeni. Na vas je, da "
"izpolnite ostalo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before you generate a puzzle, check that the settings of the "
"<guilabel>Difficulty:</guilabel> and <guilabel>Symmetry:</guilabel> drop "
"down boxes are to your liking. You can change them during a game, but then "
"they will have no effect until the next puzzle is generated."
msgstr ""
"Preden ustvarite uganko, preverite, ali so nastavitve spustnih oken "
"<guilabel>Težavnost:</guilabel> in <guilabel>Simetrija:</guilabel> po vaših "
"željah. Lahko jih spremenite med igro, vendar potem ne bodo imele učinka, "
"dokler ne ustvarite naslednje uganke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you cannot see the <guilabel>Difficulty:</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Symmetry:</guilabel> drop down boxes, use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Statusbar</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to make sure that the statusbar is "
"visible."
msgstr ""
"Če ne vidite spustnih oken <guilabel>Težavnost:</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Simetrija:</guilabel>, uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži vrstico stanja</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, da "
"zagotovite, da je vrstica stanja vidna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Difficulty:</guilabel> drop down box provides six levels of "
"difficulty, from <guimenuitem>Very Easy</guimenuitem> up to "
"<guimenuitem>Hard</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Diabolical</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>Unlimited</guimenuitem>. The easier levels may take a few "
"minutes to solve on a 9x9 board. The <guimenuitem>Hard</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>Diabolical</guimenuitem> levels may take an hour or so and are "
"intended to be equivalent to difficult grades appearing in newspapers. "
"Samurai puzzles and 16x16 or 25x25 sizes of puzzles will take longer to "
"solve, simply because there are more rows, columns and blocks and more "
"squares to fill in."
msgstr ""
"Spustni meni <guilabel>Težavnost:</guilabel> ponuja šest težavnostnih "
"stopenj, od <guimenuitem>Zelo enostavno</guimenuitem> do <guimenuitem>Težko</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Diabolično</guimenuitem> in "
"<guimenuitem>Neomejeno</guimenuitem>. Reševanje lažjih ravni lahko traja "
"nekaj minut na plošči 9x9. Stopnji <guimenuitem>Težko</guimenuitem> in "
"<guimenuitem>Diabolično</guimenuitem> lahko trajata kakšno uro in naj bi "
"bili enakovredni težkim ocenam, ki se pojavljajo v časopisih. Samurajske "
"uganke in uganke velikosti 16 x 16 ali 25 x 25 bodo reševane še dlje, "
"preprosto zato, ker je na voljo več vrstic, stolpcev in blokov ter več "
"kvadratov, ki jih je treba izpolniti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenuitem>Diabolical</guimenuitem> level typically requires one or "
"more guesses, with backtracking if you guess wrong. Lower levels can usually "
"be solved by logic alone. The <guimenuitem>Unlimited</guimenuitem> level has "
"no limits on the number of guesses required, how soon the first guess is "
"needed or how complex the logic might be. It is provided for the interest of "
"expert players, but tends to generate uninteresting <quote>inhuman</quote> "
"puzzles and is not recommended for general use."
msgstr ""
"Stopnja <guimenuitem>Diabolična</guimenuitem> običajno zahteva eno ali več "
"ugibanj, s sledenjem nazaj, če ugibate narobe. Nižje stopnje je običajno "
"mogoče rešiti zgolj z logiko. Raven <guimenuitem>Neomejeno</guimenuitem> "
"nima omejitev glede števila zahtevanih ugibanj, kako hitro je potrebno prvo "
"ugibanje ali kako zapletena je lahko logika. Na voljo je za zanimanje "
"izkušenih igralcev, vendar se nagiba k ustvarjanju nezanimivih "
"<quote>nečloveških</quote> ugank in ni priporočljivo za splošno uporabo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Symmetry:</guilabel> drop down box provides seven types of "
"symmetry, including <guimenuitem>No Symmetry</guimenuitem>. This controls "
"the layout and appearance of the squares that are filled in at the start of "
"a puzzle and has mainly aesthetic effect, except that puzzles with no "
"symmetry tend to be slightly harder than those with high symmetry and it is "
"less likely that &ksudoku; can generate a puzzle with high difficulty and "
"high symmetry combined."
msgstr ""
"Spustno polje <guilabel>Simetrija:</guilabel> ponuja sedem vrst simetrije, "
"vključno z <guimenuitem>Brez simetrije</guimenuitem>. To nadzoruje "
"postavitev in videz kvadratov, ki so izpolnjeni na začetku uganke, in ima "
"predvsem estetski učinek, le da so uganke brez simetrije nekoliko trše od "
"tistih z visoko simetrijo in manj verjetno je, da &ksudoku; lahko ustvari "
"uganko z visoko težavnostjo in visoko simetrijo skupaj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Game Menu"
msgstr "Meni igre"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starts a new game."
msgstr "Začne novo igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Load…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naloži…</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loads a saved game."
msgstr "Naloži shranjeno igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Saves</action> the current game as a default save file."
msgstr ""
"<action>Shrani</action> trenutno igro kot privzeto datoteko za shranjevanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani kot…</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Saves</action> the current game as a file of your choice."
msgstr "<action>Shrani</action> trenutno igro kot datoteko po vaši izbiri."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Natisni…</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Prints</action> the current state of a two-dimensional game on a "
"printer of your choice. The block outlines and original puzzle values are "
"printed in black. Other cells, filled-in values and solution values are "
"printed in gray. There is an option to print just one puzzle or more than "
"one puzzle per page. See <link linkend=\"configuration\">Game Configuration</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Natisne</action> trenutno stanje dvodimenzionalne igre na tiskalnik "
"po vaši izbiri. Obrisi blokov in izvirne vrednosti sestavljanke so "
"natisnjeni v črni barvi. Druge celice, izpolnjene vrednosti in vrednosti "
"rešitve so natisnjene sivo. Obstaja možnost tiskanja samo ene uganke ali več "
"ugank na stran. Glejte <link linkend=\"configuration\">Konfiguracija igre</"
"link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quits</action> &ksudoku;."
msgstr "<action>Zapusti</action> &ksudoku;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Move Menu"
msgstr "Meni Premakni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:517
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Undo</action> your last move, repeatedly if required."
msgstr "<action>Razveljavite</action> svojo zadnjo potezo, po potrebi večkrat."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ponovi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:525
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Redo</action> a move that was undone, repeatedly if required."
msgstr ""
"<action>Ponovi</action> potezo, ki je bila razveljavljena, po potrebi "
"večkrat."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>H</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Hint</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>H</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Namig</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Give a Hint</action> by filling in a vacant square."
msgstr "<action>Podajte namig</action> tako, da izpolnite prazen kvadrat."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Solve</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reši</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:540
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Instantly solve</action> the puzzle."
msgstr "<action>Takoj reši</action> uganko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:543
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Check</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preveri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Check</action> an entered puzzle for validity. If it has only one "
"solution, it becomes available for play. If it has no solution or more than "
"one solution, there has probably been an error in the data-entry."
msgstr ""
"<action>Preveri</action> veljavnost vnesene uganke. Če ima samo eno rešitev, "
"postane na voljo za igro. Če nima rešitve ali jih je več kot eno, je "
"verjetno prišlo do napake pri vnosu podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &ksudoku;…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &ksudoku;…</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Open a dialog to configure &ksudoku;.</action> See <link linkend="
"\"configuration\">Game Configuration</link> section for details."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odprite pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo &ksudoku;.</action> Za "
"podrobnosti glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"configuration\">Konfiguracija "
"igre</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:562
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &ksudoku; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &ksudoku; ima skupno &kde; Elemente menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sudoku games are traditionally played using a square grid. Themes do not "
"make much sense here, but you can select some color schemes and backgrounds. "
"To do so use <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
"&ksudoku;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> on the menubar."
msgstr ""
"Sudoku igre se tradicionalno igrajo s kvadratno mrežo. Teme tukaj nimajo "
"velikega smisla, vendar lahko izberete nekaj barvnih shem in ozadij. To "
"storite tako, da uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &ksudoku;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v "
"menijski vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam tipkovnico za igranje te igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. In &ksudoku; keyboard play is always enabled. Please use the cursor "
"keys to move the selection, numeric or alphabetic characters to enter the "
"symbols and the &Shift; key to apply markers."
msgstr ""
"Da. V &ksudoku; igranje s tipkovnico je vedno omogočeno. Uporabite smerne "
"tipke za premikanje izbire, številske ali abecedne znake za vnos simbolov in "
"&Shift; tipka za uporabo markerjev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid "Where are the high scores?"
msgstr "Kje so visoki rezultati?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ksudoku; does not have this feature."
msgstr "&ksudoku; nima te funkcije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:592
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija igre"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Options"
msgstr "Možnosti igre"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:598
#, no-c-format
msgid "When printing, try to fit more than one puzzle on a page"
msgstr "Pri tiskanju poskušajte na stran namestiti več kot eno sestavljanko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle the option to print more than one puzzle per page whenever they will "
"fit."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite možnost za tiskanje več kot ene uganke na stran, kadar koli "
"ustrezajo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, puzzles will be printed when no more will fit on "
"a page or when &ksudoku; terminates. Otherwise a puzzle is printed "
"immediately."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bodo uganke natisnjene, ko jih na stran ne bo več "
"ali ko &ksudoku; preneha. V nasprotnem primeru se uganka takoj natisne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid "Three-dimensional puzzles cannot be printed."
msgstr "Tridimenzionalnih sestavljank ni mogoče natisniti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:607
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Highlights in 2-D puzzles"
msgstr "Pokaži poudarke v 2-D ugankah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle the &ksudoku; highlight option for two-dimensional puzzles."
msgstr "Preklopite &ksudoku; možnost osvetlitve za dvodimenzionalne uganke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Errors"
msgstr "Prikaži napake"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:612
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle the option to highlight errors."
msgstr "Preklopite možnost za označevanje napak."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:615
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Highlights in 3-D puzzles"
msgstr "Prikaži poudarke v 3-D ugankah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle the &ksudoku; highlight option for three-dimensional puzzles."
msgstr "Preklopite &ksudoku; možnost osvetlitve za tridimenzionalne uganke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:619
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mathdoku puzzle size (3-9)"
msgstr "Velikost uganke Mathdoku (3-9)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:620
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose a size for Mathdoku puzzles, from 3 (very easy) to 9 (very hard) with "
"size 6 being the default."
msgstr ""
"Izberite velikost za uganke Mathdoku, od 3 (zelo enostavno) do 9 (zelo "
"težko), pri čemer je privzeta velikost 6."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings for 3-D Puzzles Only"
msgstr "Nastavitve samo za 3-D uganke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These five settings adjust the highlighting and visibility of cells in three-"
"dimensional puzzles. The idea is to make it easier to see relationships "
"between cells, especially if they are behind other cells."
msgstr ""
"Teh pet nastavitev prilagodi označevanje in vidnost celic v "
"tridimenzionalnih ugankah. Ideja je olajšati ogled odnosov med celicami, še "
"posebej, če so za drugimi celicami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Having the highlighting options enabled is recommended even for the most "
"experienced players, as it helps you see the actual game board constraints."
msgstr ""
"Omogočanje možnosti označevanja je priporočljivo tudi za najbolj izkušene "
"igralce, saj vam pomaga videti dejanske omejitve igralne plošče."

